OL,3,CElderly man killed and woman seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in crash at motorway services
OL,6,FAn elderly man has died and a woman
OL,7,Fhas been seriously injured after being
OL,8,Fin a collision with a car which also
OL,9,Fcrashed into three parked cars at
OL,10,FFleet Services.
OL,12,FThe man aged in his 80s and the woman
OL,13,Fin her 70s were hit by a blue Ford
OL,14,FExplorer in the incident which
OL,15,Fhappened at the southbound services on
OL,16,Fthe M3 at 12.44pm on Thursday. (16
OL,17,FApril)
