OL,3,CElderly man killed and woman seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in crash at motorway services
OL,6,FA Hampshire Constabulary spokesman
OL,7,Fsaid: "Police were called to a report
OL,8,Fof a blue Ford Explorer colliding with
OL,9,Fthree parked cars and two pedestrians
OL,10,Fin the southbound services.
OL,12,F"Both pedestrians ` a man in his 80s
OL,13,Fand a woman in her 70s ` sustained
OL,14,Fserious injuries.
OL,16,F"Sadly the man was pronounced deceased
OL,17,Fat the scene.
OL,19,F"His family have been notified."
