OL,3,CElderly man killed and woman seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in crash at motorway services
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Gary Doughty, from
OL,7,Fthe serious collision investigation
OL,8,Funit, said: "We are now appealing for
OL,9,Fany witnesses not already seen by
OL,10,Fpolice at the scene and anyone with
OL,11,Frelevant dash cam footage to contact
OL,12,Fus."
